period question i am on the birth control pill and my boyfriend and i use condoms however my period is a day late i know it's only a day but since i'm on the pill my cycle is predictable to the exact day and has never been late i never forget to take a pill and i always take it on time and a condom has never broken what are the chances that i'm pregnant i know it's not that late but i'm still worried since it's never happened before your chances of being pregnant are very very slim especially since your using two very effective forms of birth control i'm pretty sure you're not pregnant but if you're worried you should consider going to a doctor or taking a pregnancy test Oral contraceptive Pregnancy Fertility awareness Birth control Emergency contraception Menstrual cycle Condom Folic acid Psoriasis Endometriosis Knots Landing Apollo 8 In vitro fertilisation EastEnders Tocopherol Intrauterine device Childbirth Abortion debate Spina bifida Sedative Gonorrhoea Safe sex Urinary incontinence Human penis size Sex education Miscarriage Twin Sexual abstinence Roe v. Wade Neighbours Placebo Kodocha Obstetrics Prolactinoma Antiretroviral drug Humphrey Bogart Dr. Strangelove or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Bomb Sexual revolution Paranoia Agent Sleep Depo Provera Elephant Infertility Sex and the City Social rule Eschatology Genital wart Month Breastfeeding Days of our Lives Acne Baldness treatments CPU cache Cytomegalovirus StarCraft: Uprising Eminem Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Rape Caffeine Isotretinoin Harm reduction George Costanza Pelvic inflammatory disease Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Hypertension Teenage pregnancy Dead Like Me Oral sex Courtney Love Malaria Heartbeat (television) Morning sickness American Dreams Thalidomide Human papillomavirus Religion and abortion Randomness Chemical abortion Herpes simplex virus Menstrual cup Anencephaly Mystique (comics) Year Boston Public Abortion Premature birth Pregnancy test Melanie Wilkes I Married Marge Parti